asset.hookText:
http://www.oxo.com/p-865-muddler.aspx

The OXO SteeL Muddler crushes mint and citrus fruits for mojitos, caipirinhas, mint juleps and more. Sturdy, die-cast zinc will last years of use, and a nylon head won't scratch glasses. A soft, comfortable grip makes the Muddler easy to hold and easy to use. Cheers!
